---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About | S.E. Deracy">
    <main class="min-h-screen pt-32 pb-24 px-6 relative overflow-hidden bg-light-bg dark:bg-void-900 transition-colors duration-500">
        <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-12 opacity-10 dark:opacity-5 pointer-events-none select-none">
            <pre class="font-mono text-xs text-lilac-dark dark:text-gold leading-3">
                01010011 01000101 01000100
                01000101 01010010 01000001
                01000011 01011001 00001010
            </pre>
        </div>

        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
 
            <header class="mb-16 text-center md:text-left">
                <span class="text-lilac-dark dark:text-gold font-bold tracking-[0.2em] text-xs uppercase mb-4 block">
                    Source Code & Sorcery
                </span>
                <h1 class="heading-hero text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-6">
                    About the <span class="text-lilac-dark dark:text-gold">Architect</span>
                </h1>
            </header>

            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-12 items-start">
                
                <div class="md:col-span-5 relative group">
                    <div class="h-[90%] absolute inset-0 border-2 border-lilac dark:border-gold translate-x-4 translate-y-4 rounded-sm transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:translate-x-2 group-hover:translate-y-2 pointer-events-none"></div>
                    
                    <img 
                        src="/author.jpg" 
                        alt="S.E. Deracy" 
                        class="relative z-10 w-full h-auto grayscale hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-700 rounded-sm shadow-2xl"
                    />
                    
                    <div class="mt-12 flex justify-between text-xs font-mono text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-widest border-t border-gray-200 dark:border-void-700 pt-4">
                        <span>Class: Technomancer</span>
                        <span>Lvl: 25</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="md:col-span-7 prose prose-lg prose-headings:font-serif prose-p:text-gray-700 dark:prose-p:text-gray-300 prose-headings:text-gray-900 dark:prose-headings:text-white prose-strong:text-lilac-dark dark:prose-strong:text-gold">
                   <p class="lead text-xl text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 font-serif leading-relaxed">
                        <span class="text-lilac-dark dark:text-gold font-bold text-4xl float-left mr-3 mt-[-10px]">S.</span>
                        E. Deracy is a software engineer by day and a fantasy author by night. Fascinated by the architecture of complex systems, he applies that same rigorous logic to his writing, crafting hard magic systems where the cost of power is always strictly enforced.
                    </p>

                    <h3 class="font-bold font-serif text-lilac-dark dark:text-gold mt-4 mb-4">The Author</h3>
                    <p>
                        He has spent the last three years building the world of Eurion and writing his debut novel, <em>The Elementless Magician</em>. While he spends his days building resilient applications, his nights are dedicated to exploring the Voidâ€”a magic system that refuses to be easily categorized.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        When not writing or coding, he is likely acting as Dungeon Master for a long-running D&D campaign or getting lost in JRPGs and other video games.
                    </p>

                    <h3 class="font-bold font-serif text-lilac-dark dark:text-gold mt-4 mb-4">The Engineer</h3>
                    <p>
                        This website is not a template. It is a custom-built application engineered with the same precision as the novels.
                    </p>
                    
                    <div class="not-prose grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-4 gap-4 mt-6">
                        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-void-800 p-3 rounded text-center border border-gray-200 dark:border-void-700 shadow-sm dark:shadow-none hover:border-lilac dark:hover:border-gold/30 transition-colors">
                            <span class="block text-lilac-dark dark:text-gold font-bold text-sm">Astro</span>
                            <span class="text-[10px] text-gray-500 uppercase">Framework</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-void-800 p-3 rounded text-center border border-gray-200 dark:border-void-700 shadow-sm dark:shadow-none hover:border-lilac dark:hover:border-gold/30 transition-colors">
                            <span class="block text-lilac-dark dark:text-gold font-bold text-sm">React</span>
                            <span class="text-[10px] text-gray-500 uppercase">Interactive Map</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-void-800 p-3 rounded text-center border border-gray-200 dark:border-void-700 shadow-sm dark:shadow-none hover:border-lilac dark:hover:border-gold/30 transition-colors">
                            <span class="block text-lilac-dark dark:text-gold font-bold text-sm">Tailwind</span>
                            <span class="text-[10px] text-gray-500 uppercase">Styling</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-void-800 p-3 rounded text-center border border-gray-200 dark:border-void-700 shadow-sm dark:shadow-none hover:border-lilac dark:hover:border-gold/30 transition-colors">
                            <span class="block text-lilac-dark dark:text-gold font-bold text-sm">GitHub</span>
                            <span class="text-[10px] text-gray-500 uppercase">CI/CD</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="mt-12 pt-12 border-t border-gray-200 dark:border-void-700">
                        <h4 class="text-sm font-sans uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-500 mb-6">Connect</h4>
                        <div class="flex gap-6">
                            <a href="mailto:contact@sederacy.com" class="flex items-center gap-2 text-gray-700 dark:text-white hover:text-lilac-dark dark:hover:text-gold transition group">
                                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="w-5 h-5 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
                                <path d="M1.5 8.67v8.58a3 3 0 003 3h15a3 3 0 003-3V8.67l-8.928 5.493a3 3 0 01-3.144 0L1.5 8.67z" />
                                <path d="M22.5 6.908V6.75a3 3 0 00-3-3h-15a3 3 0 00-3 3v.158l9.714 5.978a1.5 1.5 0 001.572 0L22.5 6.908z" />
                                </svg>
                                <span>Email</span>
                            </a>

                            <a href="https://github.com/sderacy" target="_blank" class="flex items-center gap-2 text-gray-700 dark:text-white hover:text-lilac-dark dark:hover:text-gold transition group">
                                <svg class="w-5 h-5 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 0c-6.626 0-12 5.373-12 12 0 5.302 3.438 9.8 8.207 11.387.599.111.793-.261.793-.577v-2.234c-3.338.726-4.033-1.416-4.033-1.416-.546-1.387-1.333-1.756-1.333-1.756-1.089-.745.083-.729.083-.729 1.205.084 1.839 1.237 1.839 1.237 1.07 1.834 2.807 1.304 3.492.997.107-.775.418-1.305.762-1.604-2.665-.305-5.467-1.334-5.467-5.931 0-1.311.469-2.381 1.236-3.221-.124-.303-.535-1.524.117-3.176 0 0 1.008-.322 3.301 1.23.957-.266 1.983-.399 3.003-.404 1.02.005 2.047.138 3.006.404 2.291-1.552 3.297-1.23 3.297-1.23.653 1.653.242 2.874.118 3.176.77.84 1.235 1.911 1.235 3.221 0 4.609-2.807 5.624-5.479 5.921.43.372.823 1.102.823 2.222v3.293c0 .319.192.694.801.576 4.765-1.589 8.199-6.086 8.199-11.386 0-6.627-5.373-12-12-12z"/></svg>
                                <span>GitHub</span>
                            </a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>
</Layout>